snippet.title: Draft Day Sports: College Football 2022 Trailer
snippet.description:
Take over your favorite school and recruit, gameplan and call the right plays to lead them to bowl glory. Will you be able to turn your favorite school into a college football dynasty?

Learn more at https://www.wolverinestudios.com/games/draft-day-sports-college-football
